about.summary: A library for parsing, editing, and saving EXIF data

name: libexif
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "libexif" %}
{% set version = "0.6.21" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://sourceforge.net/projects/{{name}}/files/{{name}}/{{version}}/{{name}}-{{version}}.tar.gz
  sha256: edb7eb13664cf950a6edd132b75e99afe61c5effe2f16494e6d27bc404b287bf

build:
  number: 0
  skip: True  # [win]

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}
    - make

test:
  commands:
    - test -f ${PREFIX}/lib/libexif${SHLIB_EXT}  # [unix]
 
about:
  home: https://libexif.github.io/
  license: LGPL-2.1
  license_file: COPYING
  summary: 'A library for parsing, editing, and saving EXIF data'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - sebastian-luna-valero
